Beatware have released BeBasics 2.1, 
a small upgrade to the 2.0 release. Its main new feature is the ability to save in Rich Text Format. If you own 2.0 this is a free upgrade. 
BeDepot have a <A HREF="http://www.bedepot.com/shop/products/beatware/bebasics.asp">download page
</A> online, but when we checked BeDepot was off-line. 